Name: Wamu Wamu 2
About the game: Wamu Wamu 2 is a short experimental game about pieces of fruit that are infested by big worms, could you please clean them so they can be eaten? Features Around 4-8 minutes of playtime. Cute & colourful aesthetic with warm tones and soft gradients. Use 3 different tools to clean 3 pieces of fruit. It's very short, and weird, but funny? Controls Arrow keys to move. Z to jump. X to use tool. C to switch tool. Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks! Subscribe for 3$ per month at
